ng serve
    start server on localhost

ng generate component hero-detail
    create component with name 'hero-detail'
    
ng new --no-strict <app_name>
  create new angular project
  
npm install --save bootstrap@3
  inside the project folder: exec this command to install bootstrap css for this project
    this will save bootstrap in the 'node_module' folder
    then we have also to add the css stylesheet into our angular.json file in the 'styles' array. put this path there 'node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'

ng generate directive <directive_name>
  create new directive, or use ng g d
